info.title: Cafe' Amor
info.content: Welcome to Cafe' Amor, your premier destination for all things coffee! Whether you’re a die-hard espresso fan or an occasional latte sipper, we have something to suit every taste.
info.description: It is made from red beans, which are small, dark-colored beans native to Central and South America.
info.description1: Black coffee is a beverage made from roasted coffee beans.
info.description2: It's a simple drink that combines creamy dark chocolate and freshly brewed coffee.
